| 
| On amd64, you could also use
| 
|        # make libR.so visible to ld.so
|        /usr/lib64/R/lib
| 
| The run 'sudo ldconfig' and repeat 'ldd rinside_sample0'.  It should now find
| libR.so, and if so, you should be able to run all examples.
