>     |     libR.conf
>     |     (without the leading psace, though)
>     |
>     |           # make libR.so visible to ld.so
>     |           /usr/lib/R/lib
>     |
>     |     On amd64, you could also use
>     |
>     |           # make libR.so visible to ld.so
>     |           /usr/lib64/R/lib
>     |
>     |     The run 'sudo ldconfig' and repeat 'ldd rinside_sample0'.  It
>     should now
